---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Structures"
	description="Slope stability, constructional advice, and procurement support for golf course structures tied to drainage performance."
>
	<section class="section section--tight hero">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow">Services · Structures</span>
			<h1>Structural &amp; constructional engineering advice</h1>
			<p class="lede">
				Drainage problems are often tangled up with structural ones — an eroding bank, an
				undersized culvert, a failing bridge abutment. Independent engineering advice keeps these
				decisions grounded and cost-effective.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="grid grid--2">
				<div class="card">
					<h3>What's covered</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Slope stability assessment</li>
						<li>Bridge, culvert, and crossing advice</li>
						<li>Constructional detailing for drainage-related structures</li>
						<li>Procurement support — scoping work and evaluating contractor quotes</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="image-placeholder">
					Placeholder — structures/construction image
					(public/images/structures.jpg)
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section--alt">
		<div class="container" style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
			<div>
				<h2 style="margin-top:0;">Independent advice before you commit</h2>
				<p style="margin-bottom:0; max-width:34rem;">
					An independent engineering opinion before committing to a structural project can save
					significant cost — get in touch to discuss.
				</p>
			</div>
			<a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
